        <p>If you are a resident of the European Union, and you believe that our processing of your Personal Information is inconsistent with your data protection rights under the GDPR and we have not adequately addressed your concerns, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the data protection supervisory authority of your country. <a href="http://ec.europa.eu/justice/data-protection/bodies/authorities/index_en.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">http://ec.europa.eu/justice/data-protection/bodies/authorities/index_en.html</a></p>
